reviewText: Great video.  Very instructional.  The only think I don't like about it is Darin Shapiro's voice is like mono tone the whole video...kinda makes it a little boring, but the advice is great!

Great wakeboard tutorial that highlights great basic skills to work on to build a great base level of skills.  Then it shows cool big tricks and what skills you should have down to do them.  Key elments like handle placement where to be looking are awesome tips.
